    "title": {
      "rendered": "From 2005 to 2015: The Radical Effect of Social Media on Nonprofit Web Design"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Web-Design-Nonprofit-FB.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-18084\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Web-Design-Nonprofit-FB-300x300.png?resize=300%2C300\" alt=\"Web Design Nonprofit FB\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Web-Design-Nonprofit-FB.png?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Web-Design-Nonprofit-FB.png?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Web-Design-Nonprofit-FB.png?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Web-Design-Nonprofit-FB.png?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Web-Design-Nonprofit-FB.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>The average person worldwide has five social media accounts and spends an average of\u00a0<strong><a href=\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/newsbysector/mediatechnologyandtelecoms/11610959/Is-your-daily-social-media-usage-higher-than-average.html\" target=\"_blank\">1 hour and 40 minutes</a></strong> browsing these networks every day. In 2005 Facebook was only open to college students and professors, Twitter didn&#8217;t exist, and the iPhone was still in concept mode. The Internet was primarily a desktop PC or laptop experience and reading news and sending and receiving email accounted for the majority of time spent online.</p>\n<p>Today, social media consumes the most time spent on the Internet and the majority of that browsing\u00a0occurs on a smartphone or tablet. Also, over the last decade the amount of time we spend on the Internet has quadrupled. That&#8217;s radical change in a relatively short amount of time and it directly corresponds with the rapid rise of social media worldwide.</p>\n<p>Nonprofits pioneered social media. They began\u00a0actively using Myspace\u00a0in 2004 and YouTube in 2005 \u2013 years before the Fortune 500 companies. And yet despite limited budgets, the <strong><a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/2012/10/08/three-nonprofits-pioneering-responsive-web-design/\">early adopter nonprofits began using responsive web design in 2012</a></strong> in order to adapt quickly to the new realities of Internet browsing. Bold imagery. Large font. Simplified, tappable navigation and calls-to-action. Dramatic use of color. Social, shareable content. These website design trends appeal to today&#8217;s Internet users on every device, from PC to smartphone, and are required to stand out from the tens\u00a0of millions of brands active every day on social media. All that said, below are ten nonprofits embracing<strong> <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Responsive_web_design\" target=\"_blank\">responsive web design</a></strong> in 2015<strong> (<a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/2014/02/25/11-responsively-designed-nonprofit-websites-to-study-and-learn-from/\" target=\"_blank\">view 2014 list</a>)</strong> compared with their 2005 website designs.</p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">1. GlobalGiving 2015<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.globalgiving.org/\" target=\"_blank\">globalgiving.org</a></h2>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://globalngo.org/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-18042\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Global-Giving-2015-2.png?resize=600%2C271\" alt=\"Global Giving 2015 2\" width=\"600\" height=\"271\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Global-Giving-2015-2.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Global-Giving-2015-2.png?resize=300%2C135&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a>Global Giving\u00a02005<a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Global-Giving-2015-2.png\"><br />\n</a> <a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20050409070213/http://www.globalgiving.com/\" target=\"_blank\">web.archive.org/www.globalgiving.com</a></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20050409070213/http://www.globalgiving.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-18044\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Global-Giving-2005-2.png?resize=500%2C226\" alt=\"Global Giving 2005 2\" width=\"500\" height=\"226\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Global-Giving-2005-2.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Global-Giving-2005-2.png?resize=300%2C136&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">2. Hermitage Museum 2015<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hermitagemuseum.org/\" target=\"_blank\">hermitagemuseum.org</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.hermitagemuseum.org/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-18073\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Hermitage-Museum-2015.png?resize=600%2C260\" alt=\"Hermitage Museum 2015\" width=\"600\" height=\"260\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Hermitage-Museum-2015.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Hermitage-Museum-2015.png?resize=300%2C130&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Hermitage Museum 2005<br />\n<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20050802010522/http://www.hermitagemuseum.org/html_En/index.html\" target=\"_blank\">web.archive.org/www.hermitagemuseum.org</a></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20050802010522/http://www.hermitagemuseum.org/html_En/index.html\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-18074\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Hermitage-Museum-2005.png?resize=500%2C228\" alt=\"Hermitage Museum 2005\" width=\"500\" height=\"228\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Hermitage-Museum-2005.png?w=500&amp;ssl=1 500w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Hermitage-Museum-2005.png?resize=300%2C136&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">3. Human Rights Watch 2015<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hrw.org\" target=\"_blank\">hrw.org</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.hrw.org/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-18036\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Human-Rights-Watch-2015.png?resize=600%2C272\" alt=\"Human Rights Watch 2015\" width=\"600\" height=\"272\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Human-Rights-Watch-2015.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Human-Rights-Watch-2015.png?resize=300%2C136&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Human Rights Watch 2005<br />\n<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20050802075655/http://www.hrw.org/\" target=\"_blank\">web.archive.org/www.hrw.org</a></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20050802075655/http://www.hrw.org/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-18037\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Human-Rights-Watch-2005-e1438543709177.png?resize=500%2C227\" alt=\"Human Rights Watch 2005\" width=\"500\" height=\"227\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">4. International Committee of the Red Cross 2015<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.icrc.org\" target=\"_blank\">icrc.org</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.icrc.org/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-18049\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/ICRC-2015.png?resize=600%2C270\" alt=\"ICRC 2015\" width=\"600\" height=\"270\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/ICRC-2015.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/ICRC-2015.png?resize=300%2C135&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">International Committee of the Red Cross 2005<br />\n<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20050802111100/http://www.icrc.org/\" target=\"_blank\">web.archive.org/www.icrc.org</a></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20050802111100/http://www.icrc.org/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-18051\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/ICRC-2005.png?resize=500%2C227\" alt=\"ICRC 2005\" width=\"500\" height=\"227\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/ICRC-2005.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/ICRC-2005.png?resize=300%2C136&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">5. National Audubon Society 2015<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.audubon.org/\" target=\"_blank\">audubon.org</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.audubon.org/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-18078\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Audubon-2015.png?resize=600%2C271\" alt=\"Audubon 2015\" width=\"600\" height=\"271\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Audubon-2015.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Audubon-2015.png?resize=300%2C135&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">National Audubon Society\u00a02005<br />\n<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20050802111100/http://www.icrc.org/\" target=\"_blank\">web.archive.org/www.audubon.org</a></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20050802110508/http://www.audubon.org/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-18079\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Audubon-2005.png?resize=500%2C226\" alt=\"Audubon 2005\" width=\"500\" height=\"226\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Audubon-2005.png?w=500&amp;ssl=1 500w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Audubon-2005.png?resize=300%2C135&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">6. Natural Resources Defense Council 2015<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nrdc.org/\" target=\"_blank\">nrdc.org</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.nrdc.org/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-18046\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/NRDC-2015.png?resize=600%2C265\" alt=\"NRDC 2015\" width=\"600\" height=\"265\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/NRDC-2015.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/NRDC-2015.png?resize=300%2C132&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Natural Resources Defense Council 2005<br />\n<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20050802000126/http://www.nrdc.org/\" target=\"_blank\">web.archive.org/www.nrdc.org</a></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20050802000126/http://www.nrdc.org/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-18047\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/NRDC-2005.png?resize=500%2C227\" alt=\"NRDC 2005\" width=\"500\" height=\"227\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/NRDC-2005.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/NRDC-2005.png?resize=300%2C136&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">7. New York Public Library 2015<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nypl.org/\" target=\"_blank\">nypl.org</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.nypl.org/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-18062\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/NYPL-2015.png?resize=600%2C263\" alt=\"NYPL 2015\" width=\"600\" height=\"263\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/NYPL-2015.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/NYPL-2015.png?resize=300%2C131&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">New York Public Library 2005<br />\n<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20050802105933/http://www.nypl.org/\" target=\"_blank\">web.archive.org/www.nypl.org</a></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20050802105933/http://www.nypl.org/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-18063\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/NYPL-2005.png?resize=500%2C222\" alt=\"NYPL 2005\" width=\"500\" height=\"222\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/NYPL-2005.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/NYPL-2005.png?resize=300%2C133&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">8. Oceana 2015<br />\n<a href=\"http://oceana.org/\" target=\"_blank\">oceana.org</a></h2>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://oceana.org/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-18056\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Oceana-2015.png?resize=600%2C272\" alt=\"Oceana 2015\" width=\"600\" height=\"272\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Oceana-2015.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Oceana-2015.png?resize=300%2C136&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /><br />\n</a>Oceana 2005<br />\n<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20050822031303/http://www.oceana.org/\" target=\"_blank\">web.archive.org/www.oceana.org</a></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"web.archive.org/www.oceana.org\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-18057\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Oceana-2005.png?resize=500%2C226\" alt=\"Oceana 2005\" width=\"500\" height=\"226\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Oceana-2005.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Oceana-2005.png?resize=300%2C135&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">9.\u00a0Operation Smile 2015</h2>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.operationsmile.org/\" target=\"_blank\">operationsmile.org</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.operationsmile.org/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-18065\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Operations-Smile-2015.png?resize=600%2C271\" alt=\"Operations Smile 2015\" width=\"600\" height=\"271\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Operations-Smile-2015.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Operations-Smile-2015.png?resize=300%2C135&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Operation Smile 2005<br />\n<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20050802074519/http://www.operationsmile.org/\" target=\"_blank\">web.archive.org/www.operationsmile.org</a></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20050802074519/http://www.operationsmile.org/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-18071\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Operations-Smile-2005.png?resize=500%2C227\" alt=\"Operations Smile 2005\" width=\"500\" height=\"227\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Operations-Smile-2005.png?w=500&amp;ssl=1 500w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Operations-Smile-2005.png?resize=300%2C136&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">10. United Nations 2015<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.un.org/\" target=\"_blank\">un.org</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.un.org/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-18076\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/United-Nations-2015.png?resize=600%2C272\" alt=\"United Nations 2015\" width=\"600\" height=\"272\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/United-Nations-2015.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/United-Nations-2015.png?resize=300%2C136&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">United Nations 2005<br />\n<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20050802002601/http://www.un.org/english/\" target=\"_blank\">web.archive.org/www.un.org</a></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20050802002601/http://www.un.org/english/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-18077\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/United-Nations-2005.png?resize=500%2C222\" alt=\"United Nations 2005\" width=\"500\" height=\"222\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/United-Nations-2005.png?w=500&amp;ssl=1 500w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/United-Nations-2005.png?resize=300%2C133&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;\"><em>Mobile for Good: A How-To Fundraising Guide for Nonprofits</em></span></span></strong></h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Mobile-Good-How--Fundraising-Nonprofits/dp/0071825460\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft wp-image-16024\" style=\"margin: 10px; border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/mobile-for-good-look-inside.jpg?resize=99%2C150\" alt=\"mobile for good look inside\" width=\"99\" height=\"150\" /></a>Based on more than 20 years of experience and 25,000+ hours spent utilizing mobile and social media, <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Mobile-Good-How--Fundraising-Nonprofits/dp/0071825460\"><em><strong>Mobile for Good: A How-To Fundraising Guide for Nonprofits</strong></em></a> is a comprehensive 256-page book packed with more than 500 best practices. Written on the premise that all communications and fundraising are now mobile and social, Mobile for Good is a step-by-step how-to guide for writing, implementing, and maintaining a mobile and social fundraising strategy for your nonprofit.</p>\n",
